### ============================================================================
### TOOGLE MASTER - KUBERNETES API REQUESTS (AWS LOAD BALANCER)
### ============================================================================
### Use este arquivo com o DNS do Ingress Controller após o deploy no EKS.
### Todas as rotas são acessadas via um único Load Balancer (Porta 80).
### ============================================================================

# Substitua pelo DNS do seu LoadBalancer (ADDRESS obtido via: kubectl get ingress -n toogle-master)
@lb_host = http://ab4de0645d0454c1cb406eb6431474f7-d1a7169f179500d0.elb.us-east-1.amazonaws.com

# Substitua pelas chaves reais configuradas no deployment-summary.txt / Secrets
@master_key = sua_chave_mestra_aqui
@api_key = tm_key_f54b81bc161a5b84c277ed954384ae950c87adb8c795892db4abfaef75aaacab

### ============================================================================
### 1. AUTH SERVICE (Path: /auth)
### ============================================================================

### 1.1. Health Check
GET {{lb_host}}/auth/health

### 1.2. Criar nova chave de API (Requer MASTER_KEY)
# @name createKey
POST {{lb_host}}/auth/admin/keys
Authorization: Bearer {{master_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Chave de Teste EKS"
}

### 1.3. Validar chave de API
GET {{lb_host}}/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}


### ============================================================================
### 2. FLAG SERVICE (Path: /flags)
### ============================================================================

### 2.1. Health Check
GET {{lb_host}}/flags/health

### 2.2. Criar uma nova Flag
POST {{lb_host}}/flags/flags
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "new_checkout_flow",
    "description": "Ativa o novo fluxo de checkout",
    "is_enabled": true
}

### 2.3. Listar todas as Flags
GET {{lb_host}}/flags/flags
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}


### ============================================================================
### 3. TARGETING SERVICE (Path: /rules)
### ============================================================================

### 3.1. Health Check
GET {{lb_host}}/rules/health

### 3.2. Criar uma regra para uma Flag
POST {{lb_host}}/rules/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "flag_name": "new_checkout_flow",
    "is_enabled": true,
    "rules": {
        "type": "PERCENTAGE",
        "value": 50.0
    }
}


### ============================================================================
### 4. EVALUATION SERVICE (Path: /evaluate)
### ============================================================================

### 4.1. Health Check
GET {{lb_host}}/evaluate/health

### 4.2. Avaliar uma Flag para um Usuário
GET {{lb_host}}/evaluate/evaluate?flag_name=new_checkout_flow&user_id=user_12345
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}


### ============================================================================
### 5. ANALYTICS SERVICE (Path: /analytics)
### ============================================================================

### 5.1. Health Check
GET {{lb_host}}/analytics/health
